6000|$|The light {{also began}} to break in Gus's face. [...] "Ah, I know! It's {{what they do in}} war-time--signaling. They call it <b>heliographing,</b> don't they? Same thing as telegraphing, only it's done without wires. And they use the same dots and dashes, too." ...|$|R
